                     <decoNote type="decInit">Initials. Related to the style of <persName key="person_74937719" role="art">Attavente</persName>. (<ref target="https://catalog.hathitrust.org/Record/000468709">Pächt and Alexander</ref> ii. 334, pl. XXXI)</decoNote>
