                        <list>
                           <item>fol. iii verso: border, left margin, Badges of Henry VII of England among interlaced stems, foliage and flowers.</item>
                           <item>fol. 3r: frontpiece framed by a panelled border, decorated with interlaced stems, folliage, flowers, putti and medallions at intervals containing the badges of Henry VII of England and Tudor roses. The panel at the botom of the page contains four angels holding the royal arms and roses.</item>
